<HEADLINE>
TRAIN INVOLVED IN EARLIER FATALITY DERAILS IN NORTH TEXAS, 15 HURT
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By CHRISTY GONZALES and MEDE NIX 
c.1998 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
