</P>
<P>
   A9546 BC-EXP-IMPEACH-SCENE-NYT 383 21:47 U A
</P>
<P>
   WASHINGTON PUTS ON ITS SUNDAY BEST ON THE DAY AFTER
</P>
<P>
   A9540 BC-EXP-NEWSPAPER-FINANCES-MEDIA-NYT 377 21:45 U A
