<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-21 11:46 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0349 &Cx1f; taf-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-LEVENDOSKY-COLUMN-NYT     12-21 0955
