   SCI-DRUG-SHORTAGE (Undated) -- Hospitals running out of
urokinase, used to treat pulmonary embolism, heart attack, stroke
and others. FDA has found flaws in Abbott Laboratories'
manufacturing process and froze all distribution. By Richard A.
Knox. 800 words.
