<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-21 13:56 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0533 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MOVIES-PALTROW-BOS &LR;      12-21 1722
