<HEADLINE>
HURRICAN WIPES TOURISTS FROM ISLAND, BUT TOMORROW IS ANOTHER DAY 

</HEADLINE>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  (Moved in ``i'' and ``t'' categories) 
 
