Chukwu remained in critical condition at Texas Children's Hospital
on Monday, seven of them under sedation and on ventilators, and all
of them together weighing just a bit over ten pounds. By Rick
Lyman.
</P>
<P>
   NY-FIREMEN-FUNERALS (New York) _ More than 10,000 firefighters
turn out for two separate funerals of firefighters killed battling
a fire last week in Brooklyn.
