away, gets massive treatment in new TV Guide, out Monday. TV Guide
won't give us advance. This will be part one of a four-part story,
the longest in TV Guide's history, and while no one outside know
what's in it, CNN is very nervous. (Kloer, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
