by hosting North Carolina while Georgia and Georgia State also have
home games. However, the marquee matchup will feature Kentucky and
Duke in a rematch of last year's thrilling regional final won by
Kentucky. (Willingham, Atlanta-Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   BKC-GATECH-UNC _ Georgia Tech-North Carolina basketball advance.
(Arey, Atlanta-Journal-Constitution). 12.
</P>
<P>
   BKC-UGA-ECAR _ Georgia-East Carolina basketball advance.
(Schlabach, Atlanta-Journal-Constitution). 12.
</P>
<P>
   Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
</P>
