<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-21 17:59 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1105 &Cx1f; tic-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-AZR-BUDGET-AZR &LR;      12-21 0340
</HEADER>
