<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-21 21:43 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1431 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OCTUPLETS-FOLO-HNS &LR;      12-21 1347
